The paper deals with the problem of visual tracking for robotic systems, which is a topic that falls under the robotics (cs.RO) sub-category. The paper also proposes an image-space observer and an adaptive controller, which involve computer vision (cs.CV) and control systems (cs.SY) techniques. The use of adaptive control and observer-based techniques suggests that the paper may also fall under the machine learning (cs.LG) and artificial intelligence (cs.AI) sub-categories.
